Metadata-Version: 1.1
Name: seantis.kantonsrat
Version: 0.6
Summary: Specialized type and custom organisations for the Kantonsrat of Zug. 
Home-page: https://github.com/seantis/seantis.kantonsrat
Author: Seantis GmbH
Author-email: info@seantis.ch
License: GPL v2
Description: If you 
        have never heard of a Kantonsrat, this is in no way meant for you.
        
        Requirements
        ------------
        
        -  Python 2.7
        -  Plone 4.3+
        -  Linux / Posix ( Windows may or may not work )
        
